metadata.name: The Queen
metadata.description:
The Queen is an artwork dedicated to the late Queen Elizabeth. Rich in colors and lines  resulting in a beautiful remembrance of her.  
In this work you can find lots of references of her life. The preferences of colorfulness but also the love for Corgis. 

A very colorful Picasso style artwork that will look amazing on the wall of your web3 gallery or even printed on any irl wall.

Commercial use is allowed but the copyrights remains with the creator.
